- The compiled-primary ambiguity path now includes all `signal_free_adaptive_ambiguity_targets(compiled_primary_family)` pairs, not just deontic/frame special cases, and skips self-pairs to avoid redundant ambiguities in [ipfs_datasets_py/logic/modal/compiler.py#L804](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-vector-patience-8codex-gpu-1h-20260519T021015Z-codex-compiler_ambiguity-02/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_ambiguity-02-packet-000084-20260519_021727/ipfs_datasets_py/logic/modal/compiler.py#L804).
- Added focused tests for compiled-primary `frame->temporal` and `conditional_normative->deontic` ambiguity surfacing in [tests/unit_tests/logic/modal/test_modal_codec.py#L2097](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-vector-patience-8codex-gpu-1h-20260519T021015Z-codex-compiler_ambiguity-02/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_ambiguity-02-packet-000084-20260519_021727/tests/unit_tests/logic/modal/test_modal_codec.py#L2097) and [tests/unit_tests/logic/modal/test_modal_codec.py#L2191](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-vector-patience-8codex-gpu-1h-20260519T021015Z-codex-compiler_ambiguity-02/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_ambiguity-02-packet-000084-20260519_021727/tests/unit_tests/logic/modal/test_modal_codec.py#L2191).

